      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " يُصَلِّي الْإِمَامُ الظُّهْرَ يَوْمَ النَّفْرِ بِمَكَّةَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hammad, from Al Halby, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The Prayer-leader should Pray <span class=\"iTxt\">Salaat</span> Al-Zohr on the day of departure (from Mina), in Makkah’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Hammad from al-Halabiy who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘The Imam must perform Salat (prayer) of al-Zuhr on the day of departure.’” "
        ]
      }
